  "notes": "Single-page form. Customer panel is read-only/prefilled from the record-picker; Legal vs Natural field set depends on the selected customer Entity type (toggled via Transaction Type PERSON/ENTITY/ACCOUNT). The report-reason mechanism is a checkbox 'Is STR/ISTR?' + free-text 'Reason'/'Description' - there is NO discrete 'Indicators' dropdown. Each relation form (Shareholder, Director/Representative, UBO) has a collapsible 'Detail' (ID Documents) expander that rendered empty for sample records (headers not observed - NOT invented). Bank has no Detail sub-section. Shareholder offers NATURAL/LEGAL/TRUST sub-form tabs. Verbatim option-list typos preserved (SLVER, Puchase of Silve, LEASDED, TEMPORARLY, Dual ationality, MEDICAL PUPOUSES, INVESTEMENT). Dates DD/MM/YYYY; amounts numeric default 0; Rate default 1. SAVE/NEW were NOT clicked. A 'Customer is Expired' info modal appeared when selecting the Natural sample and was dismissed."
